title: SI2014
description:
Sports Illustrated Swimsuit 2014 - COMPLETE Photo and Video collection

All photos and videos were pulled directly from the SI website.

 * 1042 photos
 * All videos
 * 28 Models
 * "The Legends" Collection
 * "50 Years of Covers" Collection
 * "Zero Gravity" Photo Shoot
 * "50 Years of Swimsuit Style" Video

All photos are 1200px on the larger dimension.
All videos are in MP4 format.  
  Video: MPEG4 Video (H264) 1280x720 23.976fps [Video]
  Audio: AAC 44100Hz stereo [Audio]

Photos were ripped using Firefox.  Videos were ripped using a combination of URLSnooper, rtmpdump, and a custom Perl script.

Enjoy!
